snippet.title: LANDFALL DAY 2021 - 4 RELEASES IN ONE DAY!?
snippet.description:
On April 1st Landfall Launched TABS full release with multiplayer, A completely new game called Rounds, TABG got a complete remake and went into F2P, and Stick Fight was launched on Switch

Get Rounds: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1557740/ROUNDS
Get TABS: https://landfall.se/totally-accurate-battle-simulator
Get TABG for free: http://totallyaccuratebattlegrounds.se
Get Stick Figh on the switch: http://stickfight.se
